BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 191.76 700 Td (A MESSAGE FOR PARENTS & CAREGIVERS) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 690 m 540 690 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 660 Td (This workbook uses CBT \(Cognitive Behavioral Therapy\) principles adapted) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 643 Td (for children. It teaches kids to:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 615 Td (- Understand what anxiety is \(normalizing it\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 597 Td (- Identify their worries and triggers) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 579 Td (- Challenge anxious thoughts with evidence) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 561 Td (- Face fears gradually \(exposure therapy\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 543 Td (- Build a toolkit of calming strategies) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 510 Td (HOW TO USE: Work through pages together or let your child work) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 492 Td (independently. Go at their pace. Celebrate all brave steps!) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F1 9 Tf 72 462 Td (Copyright \(c\) 2025 Daniel Tesfamariam. All rights reserved.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
