BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 229.2 740 Td (WHAT IS ANXIETY?) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 72 700 Td (Anxiety is your brain's ALARM SYSTEM. It's supposed to keep you safe.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 72 675 Td (But sometimes the alarm goes off when there's NO real danger.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 72 650 Td (It's like a smoke alarm going off because of toast - not a fire!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 615 Td (When I feel anxious, my body might:) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 72 590 12 12 re S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 593 Td (Tummy hurts or feels funny) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 72 568 12 12 re S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 571 Td (Heart beats really fast) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 72 546 12 12 re S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 549 Td (Hands get sweaty) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 72 524 12 12 re S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 527 Td (Hard to breathe) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 72 502 12 12 re S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 505 Td (Feel dizzy) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 72 480 12 12 re S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 483 Td (Want to run away or hide) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 72 458 12 12 re S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 461 Td (Can't stop thinking scary thoughts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 424 Td (Circle the ones YOU feel! It's totally normal.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
