BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 224.4 740 Td (THE ANXIETY TRICK) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 700 Td (Here's a SECRET about anxiety:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 673 Td (The more you AVOID something scary, the SCARIER it gets!) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 72 643 Td (It's like a bully. If you run away, it chases you harder.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 72 621 Td (But if you face it \(a little bit at a time\), it gets SMALLER.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 586 Td (EXAMPLE:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 564 Td (Sarah was scared of dogs. She avoided ALL dogs.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 546 Td (Her fear got BIGGER and BIGGER.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 524 Td (Then she tried her BRAVE LADDER:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 506 Td (Step 1: Look at pictures of dogs) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 490 Td (Step 2: Watch dogs from far away) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 474 Td (Step 3: Be near a small, calm dog) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 458 Td (Step 4: Pet a friendly dog) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 90 436 Td (Each step felt scary at first, but her brain LEARNED it was safe!) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
