BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 194.64 740 Td (CALM-DOWN BREATHING EXERCISES) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 72 700 Td (BALLOON BREATH:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 678 Td (1. Put your hands on your tummy) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 660 Td (2. Breathe IN slowly - blow up the balloon in your tummy!) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 642 Td (3. Breathe OUT slowly - let the air out of the balloon) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 624 Td (4. Do this 5 times. Your body will calm down!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 72 589 Td (STAR BREATH:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 567 Td (1. Hold up your hand like a star) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 549 Td (2. With your other finger, trace UP each finger = breathe IN) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 531 Td (3. Trace DOWN each finger = breathe OUT) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 513 Td (4. By the time you finish all 5 fingers, you'll feel calmer!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 72 478 Td (HOT CHOCOLATE BREATH:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 456 Td (Pretend you're holding a cup of hot chocolate.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 438 Td (Smell the yummy chocolate \(breathe IN through nose\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 90 420 Td (Cool it down \(breathe OUT through mouth slowly\)) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
