BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 245.52 740 Td (THINKING TRAPS) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 72 705 Td (Sometimes our brains trick us into thinking the WORST will happen.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 12 Tf 72 683 Td (These are called THINKING TRAPS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 650 Td (THE DISASTER TRAP:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 632 Td (Thinking the WORST thing will definitely happen.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 614 Td ('If I raise my hand, everyone will laugh at me and I'll die of embarrassment!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 584 Td (THE ALL-OR-NOTHING TRAP:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 566 Td (Everything is either PERFECT or TERRIBLE.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 548 Td ('If I'm not the best at soccer, I'm the worst player ever!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 518 Td (THE MIND-READING TRAP:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 500 Td (Thinking you know what others think.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 482 Td ('That kid didn't wave back - they must HATE me!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 452 Td (THE FORTUNE-TELLING TRAP:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 434 Td (Predicting bad things will happen.) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F3 9 Tf 90 416 Td ('I KNOW the test will be impossible and I'll fail!') Tj ET

endstream
endobj
