BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 259.92 740 Td (PARENT GUIDE) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 700 Td (HOW TO SUPPORT YOUR ANXIOUS CHILD:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 678 Td (- Validate their feelings: 'I can see you're scared. That's okay.') Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 658 Td (- Don't accommodate avoidance - gently encourage facing fears) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 638 Td (- Model brave behavior and coping out loud) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 618 Td (- Praise EFFORT, not just outcomes \('You tried! That's so brave!'\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 598 Td (- Don't promise 'nothing bad will happen' - teach them they can COPE) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 90 578 Td (- Keep your own anxiety in check \(they mirror you\)) Tj ET
